File module:


"On new or updated file" =>triggers when a new file is created in a directory
"list"=>list all the files of a given directory
copy=>copy a file
create directory=> create a new directory
Delete=>delete a file
Read=>obtain content and metadata of a file
rename=>rename a file
write=>create a file




"On new or updated file" :
options
=>connector.working directory: base directory 
=>Directory:input directory(relative to base directory)
=>recursive :if set files indside sub directories are also considered

scheduling strategy:(fixed or cron based)
 if fixed we can further specify: scheduling frequency,start delay,timeunit
 if cron based we can specify: expression and timezone

Note:if no post action specified same file will be re-read every time it is triggered by scheduler
  



